sequenceDiagram
  participant User
  participant Detail as DSADetail
  participant Hook as useDsaTopicPage
  participant Catalog as dsa.js via dsaRegistry
  participant TopicReg as public/configs/dsa/topic-pages.json
  participant Content as public/configs/dsa/pages/*.json
  participant VizReg as visualizationRegistry.js
  participant Layout as DSATopicLayout

  User->>Detail: /dsa/:id
  Detail->>Hook: topicId
  Hook->>Catalog: getTopicById(id)
  Hook->>TopicReg: getDsaTopicPage(id)
  TopicReg-->>Hook: contentPath + visualizationId
  par Load content and visualization
    Hook->>Content: fetch JSON page body
    Hook->>VizReg: loadVisualization(id)
  end
  Content-->>Hook: header, steps, code, viz defaults
  VizReg-->>Hook: React component
  Hook-->>Layout: content + Visualization
  Layout-->>User: topic page with interactive viz
